            <div class="practice-exercise">
                <h2>üéÆ Quick Quiz</h2>
                <h3>Test Your Understanding</h3>
                
                <div class="quiz-question">
                    <p><strong>1. What is a primary key?</strong></p>
                    <label><input type="radio" name="q1"> A field that can have duplicate values</label><br>
