            <div class="summary-section">
                <h2>üéØ Key Takeaways</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>A database is an organized collection of data</li>
                    <li>Tables contain rows (records) and columns (fields)</li>
                    <li>Primary keys uniquely identify each record</li>
                    <li>DBMS software manages the database operations</li>
                    <li>CRUD operations are the foundation of data manipulation</li>
                    <li>WordPress relies on MySQL to store all its content</li>
                </ul>
